videos.description: Kansas's Devonte' Graham gets the steal, puts the ball behind his back and hammers it home.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham gets the steal and slams home the dunk

videos.description: Josh Jackson deflects the pass but the ball bounces right to Jarrett Allen for the hammer dunk.
videos.headline: Texas' Allen hammers home the dunk off lucky bounce

videos.description: Kansas gets the steal and Devonte Graham throws the lob to Legerald Vick for the huge alley-oop.
videos.headline: Kansas gets the steal leads to huge alley-oop for Vick

videos.headline: Kansas' Mason drives and makes the tough and-1 layup

videos.description: Kansas with some great passing leads to a Landon Lucas dunk over Texas defender.
videos.headline: Great ball movement by Kansas leads to Lucas dunk
